title: ‘The Sopranos’ Hall of Fame: Looking Back at “Irregular Around the Margins”
description:
The Ringer’s Bill Simmons, Van Lathan, Wosny Lambre, and Justin Sayles revisit 'The Sopranos' by looking back at Episode 5 of Season 5: “Irregular Around the Margins.”
Hosts: Bill Simmons, Van Lathan, Wosny Lambre, and Justin Sayles
Producer: Jessie Lopez
